00:00:03.803 --> 00:00:04.904 align:start position:0% line:85%
I'M HAPPY TO BE HERE.

00:00:04.937 --> 00:00:08.541 size:88% position:44% line:91%
&gt;&gt; Larry: THAT WAS SUCH AN
AMAZING THING THAT HAPPENED.

00:00:08.574 --> 00:00:10.176 line:91%
