TYPE OF THING?

00:01:40.633 --> 00:01:41.934 align:start position:0% line:85%
&gt;&gt; OH, MY GOSH.

00:01:41.967 --> 00:01:43.269 align:start position:0% line:85%
IT IS EVERYTHING.

00:01:43.302 --> 00:01:44.070 align:start position:0% line:91%
EVERY PIECE OF PAPER THAT COMES
HOME.

00:01:44.103 --> 00:01:45.771 align:start position:0% line:85%
EVERY ASSIGNMENT.

00:01:45.804 --> 00:01:47.005 align:start position:0% line:91%
I MEAN, DIG THROUGH THAT
BACKPACK.

00:01:47.039 --> 00:01:50.877 align:start position:0% line:91%
MAKE IT YOUR BUSINESS TO FIND
OUT WHAT THEY WERE TEACHING THEM

00:01:50.910 --> 00:01:51.677 align:start position:0% line:85%
EVERY SINGLE DAY.

